c two-spin correlation functions are short\nranged with the correlation length proportional to $1/\\ln(1+|J_1|/J)$.\nDynamical spin susceptibilities are discussed and it is shown that the soft\nmode can be observed experimentally in the longitudinal channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Apr 2012 07:40:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2012 08:15:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2012 05:57:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-25"}
