 also increase\nlinearly with $\\ln \\sqrt{s}$ for both data and the models studied. The rate of\nincrease in cluster size vs. $\\ln \\sqrt{s}$ from models studied are larger\ncompared to those from the data and higher for PHOJET compared to PYTHIA. Our\nstudy indicates that the forward-backward measurements will provide a clear\ndistinguishing observable for the models studied at LHC energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Apr 2012 10:06:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
